articles.title: Hungary’s PM Orban meets Russia’s Putin in a Moscow visit condemned by Ukraine and EU leaders - CNN
articles.description: Hungarian Prime Minister Viktor Orban traveled to Moscow on Friday to meet Russian President Vladimir Putin, causing major outrage among his fellow European Union leaders.
